id":51951,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老實d講 我利申先 皇馬迷<br />\n成隊波冇起色 拖舟真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣乜鳩morata <br />\n有前鋒用咩 <br />\n一月唔增兵 真係皆空</blockquote><br />\nmorata今季皆空機會遠大於皇馬，皇馬依家專心歐聯西盃，應該雙料冠軍了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔識分你曲定圓<br />\n雙料冠軍都講得出 人唔笑狗都吠啦 垃圾蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知除咗皇馬，依家歐洲好多隊都專心歐聯<br />\n英超無望嘅曼聯，車，利，熱，<br />\n喺聯賽獨大，可以充分準備歐聯嘅曼城，拜仁，巴黎<br />\n不過皇馬有牙朗米露拉膠，質素始終高一班，你入皇區睇吓，好多都抱住專心盃賽必勝嘅信念"},{"pid":"47b50d8c5e90a6d1d7d7ef1b15d54430b4721bd1","tid":508141,"uid":154756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"保連奴得7分?"},{"pid":"128f4ca133beb8745a364be464a455627f451218","tid":508141,"uid":7245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ag 7分<br />\nso9 6分<br />\n屌你呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBullshitGC都係得6分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5664cb3a623cf33e067dd6a03898256123de10","tid":508141,"uid":36701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老實d講 我利申先 皇馬迷<br />\n成隊波冇起色 拖舟真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣乜鳩morata <br />\n有前鋒用咩 <br />\n一月唔增兵 真係皆空</blockquote><br />\nmorata今季皆空機會遠大於皇馬，皇馬依家專心歐聯西盃，應該雙料冠軍了</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔識分你曲定圓<br />\n雙料冠軍都講得出 人唔笑狗都吠啦 垃圾蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心戰王都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd14626f6234324435d85b0322468aea845e7f6","tid":508141,"uid":51951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1